data.description: Looking for a new place to call home? You've found it! Nestled on a coveted corner lot, this beauty flaunts a beautiful façade with stone accents, a lush green landscape, a 2-car garage, and a welcoming porch! Inside, you will find a spacious living area with vaulted ceilings, polished wood flooring, and a warm fireplace perfect for cold evenings. Prepare delicious meals in this eat-in kitchen, comprised of staggered cabinetry with crown moulding, built-in appliances, a handy pantry, and a prep island. Don't forget about the sizeable den, ideal for an office. Discover a cozy primary bedroom boasting soft carpet and a private ensuite for added comfort. The HUGE basement has all the potential to become a family room, entertainment area, or anything else you can imagine! Also included is a quaint backyard patio where you can sit back and enjoy a relaxing evening or have fun BBQs. Right across the street are schools, a park and a new disk golf course.  Don't forget about the walking/running trails, just down the street. This home has it all! Act now before it's gone!
